                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261207-70-off418 t18261207-70-cd419"></join>, 1 coat, value 5s.; 1 cloak, value 5s; 7 pairs of stockings, value 7s.; 2 razors, value 5s.; 1 stock, value 2s.; 1 handkerchief, value 1s.; 1 spoon, value 2s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
