                     <interp inst="t18261207-70-person524" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a watchman. I found the other property on the prisoner; he is a stranger; he had no money, and appeared in poverty.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18261207-70-person525">
